<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting" />
    <title>Tender Received Notification</title>
    <style>
        body,
        table,
        td,
        a {
            text-size-adjust: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, Roboto, Inter, sans-serif;
            color: #3a3e49;
            background: #f4f4f4;
        }

        table {
            border-collapse: collapse !important;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .email-header {
            background: #0090F3;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px 20px;
        }

        .email-header img {
            width: 160px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 30px 40px;
            color: #3a3e49;
        }

        .email-body h2 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0090F3;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .email-body p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #555;
        }

        .status-label {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background-color: #17a2b8;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 6px;
            background-color: #0090F3;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background: #0078DC;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background: #3a3e49;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <center>
        <table class="email-container">
            <tr>
                <td class="email-header">
                    <img src="{{backend_url}}/images/defaults/app-logo.svg" alt="{{company_name}} Logo" />
                    <h1>Tender Acknowledgment</h1>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td class="email-body">
                    <h2>Hello, {{organization_name}}</h2>

                    <p>We would like to inform you that your submission for the tender <strong>{{tender_title}}</strong>
                        has been successfully <strong>received</strong> by the posting organization
                        <strong>{{posted_by}}</strong>.</p>

                    <p>
                        <span class="status-label">RECEIVED</span>
                    </p>

                    <p>This acknowledges that your tender has been submitted and is now in the review phase.</p>

                    <p>You can view the submitted tender details by clicking the link below:</p>

                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <a href="{{tender_url}}" class="button">View Your Submission</a>
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td class="email-footer">
                    &copy; {{year}} {{company_name}}. All rights reserved.
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </center>
</body>

</html>